name: The Dark Descent - Slipcase CD
description:
New album available in CD and Slipcase CD versions.

8 Haunting tracks of crushing, old-school Black Metal that merges with modern, unearthly influences and results in a unique, mind blowing new level of metal madness.  

The album features vocals by Mysteriis (Setherial) 
and guitar solos by Bernd "Bernth" Brodträger (Belphegor) 
and Fabio Zperandio (Ophiolatry).

This album represents a new chapter in the history of the band and offers new, more complex songwriting elements, without sacrificing any of the merciless, blasting pace for which the group is well-known.  From the highest spheres to the deepest abyss, "The Dark Descent" is a enigmatic journey that extends into the outermost boundaries of the mind.


AVAILABLE SOON !! 

Contact us via email for info:  divinecodex@gmail.com
